{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224700/extras/Big_CIty.gif?t=1729260848\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to explore Throw Island as you, jump, slide, and most importantly, throw your way to victory. Throw Bro is a challenging, GameBoy-style, 2D platforming game where you use your enemies against them by throwing them at each other. As you play you will find many unique secrets and puzzles and ultimately find out who took Throw Gal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore 4 of our favorite levels from the first few worlds of Throw Bro in this demo! Get to meet the characters and see several mechanics featured throughout the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare to hone your throwing skills to take down some tough opponents. Throw Bro has many boss fights, each one challenging your skills in different and unique ways. Get ready to dodge and throw to put an end to the evil-doers of Throw Island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224700/extras/Lance.gif?t=1729260848\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throwing items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dashing ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sliding ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speedrunning Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many hidden secrets in each world that you will have to discover for yourself</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We hope you can enjoy Throw Bro and the care that was put into the gameplay, story, art, and music. Get ready, and go throw!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224700/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729260848",